{"pin":"BH00868","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00868","anchor":"","first_line":"In this day, praise and salutations and remembrance and utterance are reserved unto the chosen ones of God, exalted be His glory, who have dispelled the doubts of the people [3.5s]... ...My God, Whom I worship and adore! I bear witness unto Thy unity and Thy oneness, and acknowledge Thy gifts","first_line_orig":"امروز ثنا و سلام و ذکر و بیان مخصوص اولیاء حق جل جلاله است که شبهات اهل  ","language":"5","word_count":"940","subjects":"@prayer for forgiveness, @prayer for spiritual recognition, @rejection by the people of the Bayan, @praise and encouragement, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @heedlessness and ignorance of the people","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#503\"\u003eLL#503\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"}]},{"code":"BH00868GOD","anchor":"god","translations":[{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"}]},{"code":"BH00868WIT","anchor":"wit","translations":[{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"nl","lang